        " «لاَ بَأْسَ إِذَا كَانَ فِي حَالِ اَلتَّقِيَّةِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.835 - Ali ibn Yaqtin asked Imam Abu al-Hasan al-Awwal (as) about a man prostrating on a misḥ (a type of mat or rug) and on a carpet.\nThe Imam said: \"There is no issue if it is in a situation of taqiyya (precautionary dissimulation to protect oneself).\""
        ]
      }
    },
